    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/getting-started-with-generative-ai-hub-on-sap-ai-core/ev-p/14090952</id>
    <title>🇬🇪 Getting started with Generative AI Hub on SAP AI Core</title>
    <updated>2025-05-01T00:47:59.410000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Vitaliy-R</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/183</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;FONT color="#FF0000"&gt;*** REGISTRATION FOR THIS EVENT IS NOW CLOSED ***&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;This&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://groups.community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/gh-p/code-jam" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;SAP CodeJam&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;event is on&amp;nbsp;&lt;SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Getting Started with Generative AI Hub on SAP AI Core&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;and Python. You do not need any background in the topic, but you should have&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;a lot of curiosity!&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;In this CodeJam, you will learn how to use the Generative AI Hub on SAP AI Core to implement retrieval-augmented generation (RAG). This approach improves the responses of large language models (LLMs) and reduces hallucinations. You will learn how to deploy an LLM and the orchestration service on SAP AI Core, and how to query it via SAP AI Launchpad and the Python SDK. Additionally, you will gain insights into key generative AI concepts and learn how to enhance RAG responses.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;This is a&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;free&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;in-person event&lt;/STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;and is planned for&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;Thursday, May 29th&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;in&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;Tbilisi, Georgia&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="lia-unicode-emoji" title=":georgia:"&gt;🇬🇪&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;from&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;11:00 to 17:00 GET&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;.&amp;nbsp;The language of the event and the content will be in English.&amp;nbsp;The instructor is&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/developer-advocates.html" target="_self" rel="noreferrer noopener"&gt;Developer Advocate&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;A href="https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/183" target="_blank"&gt;@Vitaliy-R&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/STRONG&gt;from&lt;STRONG&gt;&amp;nbsp;SAP.&lt;/STRONG&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;The event is kindly hosted by&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;EPAM&lt;/STRONG&gt;. Thank you!&lt;/P&gt;&lt;H6 id="toc-hId--2068589778"&gt;EPAM Georgia, 10 Bidzina Kvernadze St,&lt;BR /&gt;Tbilisi 0171, Georgia&lt;/H6&gt;&lt;P&gt;Please note that spaces are limited; we can only accommodate&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;25 attendees&lt;/STRONG&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;FONT color="#FF0000"&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;*** REGISTRATION FOR THIS EVENT IS NOW CLOSED ***&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Prerequisites:&amp;nbsp;&lt;SPAN&gt;Any Chromium-based web browser, such as Vivaldi, Brave, Microsoft Edge, Google Chrome etc.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;EM&gt;Visit the SAP&lt;A href="https://groups.community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/gh-p/code-jam" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;&amp;nbsp;CodeJam group&lt;/A&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;for more information on SAP CodeJam events, to ask questions, and to chat with your fellow attendees.&lt;/EM&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/sap-codejam/getting-started-with-generative-ai-hub-on-sap-ai-core/ev-p/14090952"/>
    <published>2025-05-01T00:47:59.410000+02:00</published>
